OL,6,F"We'd take the stuff back, we'd drive
OL,7,Fback around to this side of town and
OL,8,Fdo the same here.
OL,10,F"There's certain opticians up here,
OL,11,Fpharmacies, clothing shops, that were
OL,12,Fhit frequently. I would average
OL,13,Fanything from #2000 to #4000 in retail
OL,14,Fprice."
OL,16,FCullan's reason for doing this was
OL,17,Fsimple, he was making enough money to
OL,18,Ffeed his addiction to heroin.
