OL,6,FHe has since beaten this addiction,
OL,7,Fand without the need to buy drugs to
OL,8,Ffeed his habit, he has also stopped
OL,9,Fshoplifting.
OL,11,FHe said: "At the time I felt like it
OL,12,Fwas a badge of honour, like I'm good
OL,13,Fat doing this. Looking back on it,
OL,14,Fit's shameful.
OL,16,F"It doesn't worry me anymore because
OL,17,FI've paid my dues, anything that I've
OL,18,Fdone I've been caught for, I've done
OL,19,Fmy time for."
