OL,6,FWhile Cullan has recovered from his
OL,7,Faddiction, shoplifting figures in
OL,8,FWales continue to rise.
OL,10,FMore than 21,000 cases of retail theft
OL,11,Fwere recorded by police forces in
OL,12,FWales last year, an increase of 36%
OL,13,Ffrom the previous year, higher than
OL,14,Fany other country in the UK.
OL,16,FThat increase is having an impact on
OL,17,Fboth businesses and their employees.
