OL,6,FViolence and intimidation are widely
OL,7,Freported, and there are fears police
OL,8,Fare struggling to help tackle the
OL,9,Fproblem.
OL,11,FAs far as Cullan is concerned,
OL,12,Fpunishment doesn't work. Instead,
OL,13,Fpreventing the causes of crimes such
OL,14,Fas shoplifting should be the priority.
OL,16,F"I've been to jail ten times for
OL,17,Fshoplifting," he continued. "The
OL,18,Fpenalties they have in place right
OL,19,Fnow, it just aren't working.
