OL,4,Cshoplifting, punishment doesn't work'
OL,6,F"People are getting caught for a
OL,7,Fcouple of bottles from a shop, they're
OL,8,Fgoing to jail for four weeks then
OL,9,Fthey're coming out and going straight
OL,10,Fback to the same shop and doing it
OL,11,Fagain.
OL,13,F"What I would say is we're seeing a
OL,14,Fpattern of behaviour with people who
OL,15,Fshoplift and we need to do something
OL,16,Felse apart from sending these people
OL,17,Fto prison.
OL,19,F"I think it should be more of a health
OL,20,Fissue if it's driven by addiction."
