OL,6,FDr Frederick Cram is the director of
OL,7,Fthe Centre for Crime, Law and Justice
OL,8,Fat
OL,10,FHe studies an approach known as
OL,11,F'Integrated Offender Management', a
OL,12,Fform of rehabilitation of persistent
OL,13,Foffenders within the community.
OL,15,F"Mainly people are shoplifting for
OL,16,Fdrugs, and so that requires a response
OL,17,Fthat tackles that need that that
OL,18,Fperson has around substance misuse,"
OL,19,Fhe told ITV Cymru Wales.
