OL,8,FGovernment's Home Office.
OL,10,FIn October the National Police Chiefs'
OL,11,FCouncil launched its Retail Crime
OL,12,FAction Plan.
OL,14,FIn a statement, the Home Office said:
OL,15,F"Progress is being made through a
OL,16,Fpolice commitment to prioritise
OL,17,Fattending the scene of shoplifting
OL,18,Finstances involving violence against a
OL,19,Fshop worker, which is an aggravating
OL,20,Ffactor and carries tougher sentences
OL,21,Ffor offenders."
